				Have you ever wondered how to add comments to your index page? A client wanted their visitors to be able to leave a comment on an article without having to press a link? 

I'm still working through the pros and cons for this but I went ahead and added it to the site.  I have to say it adds an element of UX that was not there before.  Convenience is a big factor for some visitors to interact.&nbsp;

You can find out how to do this <a href="http://seoporch.com/add-comments-to-the-index-page-in-wordpress/">here at SEOPorch.com</a>
